useVConsole ​

Category
@Integrations
Package
comuse/integrations
Last Changed
8月15日16时0分

Wrapper for vconsole.

Install ​

bash
npm i vconsole

Usage ​

ts
import { useVConsole } from 'comuse-integrations/useVConsole'

const vConsole = useVConsole({
  hostname: ['ajiu9.cn']
})

or

ts
import { useVConsole } from 'comuse-integrations/useVConsole'

const vConsole = useVConsole({
  debug: true
})
